stateful is when system bring "state"

being stateful system meaning that if the instance or package dies, when it restart or restransmit, it will still working. There is no "state" lost.

Example:
TCP -- it has state to deliver between two instance to establish connection
WebSocket
QUIC
Product service -- it has state to saved on the database

**note: you can build stateful protocol upon stateless protocol (ex: QUIC -- UDP)
